## About
Testing extensions for macOS / iOS

## Installation

[![Carthage compatible](https://img.shields.io/badge/Carthage-compatible-4BC51D.svg?style=flat)](https://github.com/Carthage/Carthage)

```
// Cartfile
github "larromba/testextensions" ~> 1.0
```

```
// Terminal
carthage update
```
